<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="favicon.svg">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>SATOI コンシェルジュ - 誰かに、話したい時</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@300;400;500;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --night-deep: #0B1736;
  --night-medium: #1A2548;
  --starlight: #D4A95E;
  --starlight-strong: #F0C97A;
  --morning-white: #FBF7F0;
  --morning-cream: #F6EFE3;
  --teal: #0D7377;
  --teal-soft: #14A6AB;
  --healing-blue: #7FA8C9;
  --warm-orange: #D4622A;
  --warm-coral: #E08461;
  --rose: #C76B7F;
  --ink-deep: #1A2A40;
  --ink-medium: rgba(26,42,64,0.78);
  --ink-light: rgba(26,42,64,0.55);
  --line: rgba(10,22,40,0.10);
  --font: "Noto Sans JP", "Meiryo UI", "Hiragino Kaku Gothic ProN", sans-serif;
}
* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
html, body { width: 100%; min-height: 100vh; overflow-x: hidden; font-family: var(--font); }
body { color: var(--morning-white); background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0B1736 0%, #1A2548 60%, #2E1F45 100%); line-height: 1.85; font-size: 16px; }
button { font-family: var(--font); cursor: pointer; }

.header { position: fixed; top:0; left:0; right:0; z-index:100; padding: 16px 32px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; background: rgba(11,23,54,0.92); backdrop-filter: blur(14px); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(248,246,240,0.08); }
.logo { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.22em; color: var(--morning-white); display: inline-flex; align-items: center; text-decoration: none; }
.logo .dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; background: var(--teal-soft); border-radius: 50%; margin-right: 10px; box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--teal-soft); }
.back-btn { padding: 8px 18px; background: rgba(248,246,240,0.08); color: var(--morning-white); border: 1px solid rgba(248,246,240,0.22); border-radius: 20px; font-size: 12px; }

.hero { padding: 130px 32px 50px; text-align: center; }
.hero-eyebrow { display: inline-block; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.42em; color: var(--teal-soft); padding: 6px 18px; border: 1px solid rgba(20,166,171,0.4); border-radius: 24px; margin-bottom: 22px; }
.hero-title { font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 42px); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.55; letter-spacing: 0.06em; margin-bottom: 18px; }
.hero-title strong { color: var(--starlight-strong); font-weight: 500; }
.hero-sub { font-size: 15px; color: rgba(248,246,240,0.85); line-height: 2; max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; }

.routes { max-width: 1080px; margin: 30px auto 60px; padding: 0 24px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px; }

/* 電話ルート */
.route-phone {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(212,98,42,0.18), rgba(199,107,127,0.18));
  border: 2px solid rgba(212,98,42,0.5);
  border-radius: 24px;
  padding: 36px 32px;
  text-align: center;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.route-phone::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute; top: -30%; right: -30%;
  width: 280px; height: 280px;
  background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(212,98,42,0.25), transparent 70%);
  border-radius: 50%;
}
.route-icon-big {
  width: 86px; height: 86px;
  margin: 0 auto 22px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: rgba(212,98,42,0.25);
  border: 2px solid rgba(212,98,42,0.6);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 36px;
  position: relative; z-index: 2;
  animation: phoneRing 2s infinite;
}
@keyframes phoneRing {
  0%, 100% { transform: scale(1) rotate(0); }
  10% { transform: scale(1.08) rotate(-8deg); }
  20% { transform: scale(1.08) rotate(8deg); }
  30% { transform: scale(1) rotate(0); }
}
.route-title { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 10px; color: var(--starlight-strong); position: relative; z-index: 2; }
.route-desc { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(248,246,240,0.85); line-height: 1.95; margin-bottom: 22px; position: relative; z-index: 2; }
.route-phone-number {
  display: block;
  font-size: 28px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--morning-white);
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
  position: relative; z-index: 2;
}
.route-phone-hours { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(248,246,240,0.7); margin-bottom: 22px; position: relative; z-index: 2; }
.route-call-btn {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 16px 36px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D4622A, #E08461);
  color: white;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 28px;
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  text-decoration: none;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(212,98,42,0.4);
  transition: all 0.3s;
  position: relative; z-index: 2;
}
.route-call-btn:hover { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E08461, #F0C97A); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 14px 36px rgba(212,98,42,0.55); }

/* AIチャットルート */
.route-ai {
  background: rgba(248,246,240,0.06);
  border: 2px solid rgba(212,169,94,0.4);
  border-radius: 24px;
  padding: 36px 32px;
  text-align: center;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}
.route-ai .route-icon-big {
  background: rgba(212,169,94,0.20);
  border-color: rgba(212,169,94,0.6);
  animation: none;
}
.ai-chat-btn {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 16px 36px;
  background: var(--starlight);
  color: var(--night-deep);
  border: none;
  border-radius: 28px;
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  margin-top: auto;
}
.ai-chat-btn:hover { background: var(--starlight-strong); }

/* チャットUI */
.chat-wrap {
  max-width: 820px;
  margin: 0 auto 80px;
  padding: 0 24px;
  display: none;
}
.chat-wrap.show { display: block; }
.chat-box {
  background: rgba(248,246,240,0.06);
  border-radius: 22px;
  padding: 28px 28px 24px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(248,246,240,0.12);
}
.chat-eyebrow { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.32em; color: var(--starlight); margin-bottom: 16px; text-align: center; }
.chat-history {
  background: rgba(11,23,54,0.6);
  border-radius: 14px;
  padding: 22px;
  min-height: 320px;
  max-height: 480px;
  overflow-y: auto;
  margin-bottom: 18px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 14px;
}
.chat-msg { display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: flex-start; }
.chat-msg-ai { }
.chat-msg-user { flex-direction: row-reverse; }
.chat-avatar {
  width: 36px; height: 36px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;
}
.chat-msg-ai .chat-avatar { background: var(--starlight); color: var(--night-deep); }
.chat-msg-user .chat-avatar { background: var(--teal-soft); color: white; }
.chat-bubble {
  padding: 12px 18px;
  border-radius: 16px;
  font-size: 13.5px;
  line-height: 1.85;
  max-width: 75%;
}
.chat-msg-ai .chat-bubble { background: rgba(248,246,240,0.10); color: var(--morning-white); border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; }
.chat-msg-user .chat-bubble { background: rgba(20,166,171,0.18); color: var(--morning-white); border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; }

.chat-input-row { display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center; }
.chat-input {
  flex: 1;
  padding: 14px 20px;
  background: rgba(248,246,240,0.06);
  border: 1px solid rgba(248,246,240,0.18);
  border-radius: 26px;
  color: var(--morning-white);
  font-family: var(--font);
  font-size: 14px;
  outline: none;
}
.chat-input:focus { border-color: var(--starlight); background: rgba(248,246,240,0.10); }
.chat-input::placeholder { color: rgba(248,246,240,0.5); }
.chat-send {
  padding: 14px 24px;
  background: var(--starlight);
  color: var(--night-deep);
  border: none;
  border-radius: 26px;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 500;
}
.chat-send:hover { background: var(--starlight-strong); }
.chat-mic {
  width: 46px; height: 46px;
  background: rgba(212,98,42,0.15);
  border: 1px solid rgba(212,98,42,0.45);
  color: var(--starlight-strong);
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
}
.chat-mic:hover { background: rgba(212,98,42,0.30); }
.chat-mic svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; fill: none; stroke: currentColor; stroke-width: 2; }

.chat-quick {
  display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 14px;
}
.chat-quick-btn {
  padding: 6px 14px;
  background: rgba(248,246,240,0.06);
  border: 1px solid rgba(248,246,240,0.18);
  color: rgba(248,246,240,0.85);
  border-radius: 16px;
  font-size: 11.5px;
}
.chat-quick-btn:hover { background: var(--starlight); color: var(--night-deep); border-color: var(--starlight); }

.chat-call-hint {
  margin-top: 18px;
  padding: 14px 18px;
  background: rgba(212,98,42,0.10);
  border-left: 3px solid var(--warm-orange);
  border-radius: 10px;
  font-size: 12.5px;
  color: rgba(248,246,240,0.85);
}
.chat-call-hint a { color: var(--starlight-strong); text-decoration: underline; }

/* 安心メッセージ */
.assure {
  max-width: 880px; margin: 0 auto 80px; padding: 0 24px;
  text-align: center;
}
.assure-text {
  font-size: 13.5px; color: rgba(248,246,240,0.78); line-height: 2;
  padding: 22px 28px;
  background: rgba(248,246,240,0.04);
  border-radius: 16px;
  border: 1px dashed rgba(248,246,240,0.20);
}
.assure-text strong { color: var(--starlight-strong); }

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .routes { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .hero { padding: 100px 16px 40px; }
  .route-phone, .route-ai { padding: 28px 22px; }
  .route-phone-number { font-size: 22px; }
}

/* === SATOI 共通リッチトースト === */
#satoi-toast-host { position: fixed; bottom: 24px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); z-index: 9999; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; pointer-events: none; max-width: 92vw; }
.satoi-toast { pointer-events: auto; min-width: 280px; max-width: 480px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(11,23,54,0.96), rgba(26,37,72,0.96)); color: #F8F6F0; padding: 16px 22px 16px 18px; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(11,23,54,0.35), 0 0 0 1px rgba(212,169,94,0.30); font-family: "Noto Sans JP", "Meiryo UI", sans-serif; font-size: 13.5px; line-height: 1.75; backdrop-filter: blur(14px); display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: flex-start; opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); transition: all 0.4s; border-left: 3px solid #D4A95E; }
.satoi-toast.show { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.satoi-toast.success { border-left-color: #14A6AB; }
.satoi-toast.warn { border-left-color: #D4622A; }
.satoi-toast-icon { flex-shrink: 0; width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(212,169,94,0.18); display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
.satoi-toast-body { flex: 1; }
.satoi-toast-close { background: transparent; border: none; color: rgba(248,246,240,0.5); cursor: pointer; font-size: 18px; padding: 2px 4px; }
#satoi-univ-nav { position: fixed; top: 50%; right: 14px; transform: translateY(-50%); z-index: 9998; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; pointer-events: none; }
.satoi-univ-btn { pointer-events: auto; width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(11,23,54,0.85); color: #F0C97A; border: 1px solid rgba(212,169,94,0.4); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; cursor: pointer; font-size: 16px; backdrop-filter: blur(10px); transition: all 0.3s; box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(11,23,54,0.25); font-family: inherit; }
.satoi-univ-btn:hover { background: #D4A95E; color: #0B1736; transform: scale(1.1); }
.satoi-lang-pop { position: absolute; right: 54px; top: 0; background: rgba(11,23,54,0.94); border: 1px solid rgba(212,169,94,0.4); border-radius: 12px; padding: 6px; min-width: 130px; display: none; flex-direction: column; gap: 2px; }
.satoi-lang-pop.show { display: flex; }
.satoi-lang-opt { padding: 8px 14px; border-radius: 8px; color: #F8F6F0; font-size: 12px; cursor: pointer; text-align: left; background: transparent; border: none; font-family: inherit; }
.satoi-lang-opt:hover { background: rgba(212,169,94,0.18); color: #F0C97A; }
.satoi-lang-opt.active { background: rgba(212,169,94,0.25); color: #F0C97A; font-weight: 600; }
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  html { font-size: 15px; }
  #satoi-univ-nav { right: 8px; bottom: 80px; top: auto; transform: none; }
  .satoi-univ-btn { width: 40px; height: 40px; font-size: 14px; }
  input, textarea, select { font-size: 16px !important; }
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="header">
  <a href="SATOI_Mock_v1_A1_entrance.html" class="logo"><span class="dot"></span>SATOI ・ コンシェルジュ</a>
  <button class="back-btn" onclick="history.back()">← 戻る</button>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-eyebrow">SATOI CONCIERGE</div>
  <h1 class="hero-title">うまく言葉にできなくて、<br><strong>でも、誰かに話したい時</strong>。</h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">
    告知から間もない方・どこから手をつけたら良いか分からない方へ。<br>
    <strong>AIチャット</strong> でゆっくり整理するか、<strong>電話</strong> で直接話すか、選べます。
  </p>
</section>

<!-- 2つの選択肢 -->
<div class="routes">
  <div class="route-phone">
    <div class="route-icon-big">📞</div>
    <div class="route-title">電話で、話す</div>
    <div class="route-desc">24時間365日、SATOI コンシェルジュが直接お話を伺います。<br>「何を話せばいいか分からない」のままで大丈夫です。</div>
    <span class="route-phone-number">0120-1234-5678</span>
    <div class="route-phone-hours">通話料無料 ・ 24時間 ・ 365日 対応</div>
